item.title: CVE-2019-9491|2024-08-04T21:54:44.137Z -- trend%20micro -- trend%20micro%20anti-threat%20toolkit%20%28attk%29
item.description: Trend Micro Anti-Threat Toolkit (ATTK) versions 1.62.0.1218 and below have a vulnerability that may allow an attacker to place malicious files in the same directory, potentially leading to arbitrary remote code execution (RCE) when executed.
